document.full_text: mahesh bhupathi and leander paes of india, the world's third-ranked doubles team, tumbled out of the french open saturday in a straight set upset loss to stephen huss and ashley fisher of australia, 7-6 (7), 6-4.
document.title: bhupathi and paes are eliminated
